item.title: Teaching
item.description: This page contains the teaching material for courses I have taught and developed. At the links below, you’ll find slides, assignments, and other resources. Feel free to use them. Research Methods This is an undergraduate criminology and criminal justice research methods course. This course was adapted from the Justin Nix’s CRCJ 2510 Research Methods course. GitHub: https://github.com/nvietto/Teaching/tree/main/CRCJ-2510 Applied Statistics This is an undergraduate criminology and criminal justice applied statistics course.
